summaries.short: Sofia struggles to keep her business legal.
summaries.full: Sofia reaches a temporary agreement with Lucia and the investor’s father, but she discovers he might be laundering money. SofiX hosts a premiere for a government official. Julio asks Sofia to make a donation for the environment and she creates AmazonX, the first porn non-profit.

summaries.short: Sofia faces jail time to save her company and her marriage.
summaries.full: Unbeknownst to Sofia, Violeta’s boyfriend Guto is cast at SofiX for an adult movie. In a risky move, Sofia engages Andrea’s and Lucia’s help to expose the investors. Marcello and Sofia return from vacation with a surprise but receive bad news from the police department.

summaries.short: Sofia sets boundaries with Marcello and the kids while figuring out the future of SofiX.​
summaries.full: SofiX’s new investors threaten Sofia. Marcello celebrates his upcoming fatherhood with his friends and returns to old habits. Sofia sets boundaries with her kids and cancels the wedding. Haru helps Sofia find dirt about the investors to counter their threats.

summaries.short: Sofia backpedals on the company’s sale and her wedding plans, but it might be too late.
summaries.full: ​Marcello begs Sofia not to sell SofiX while Sofia asks Lucia to help her reverse the deal and save her employees’ jobs. Victoria makes an unexpected announcement and Sofia’s mother takes over her wedding plans. Sofia asks Andrea for advice on her son’s sexuality.

summaries.short: Sofia brings in a new investor and receives important news about her health.
summaries.full: Suspecting her family might be growing, Sofia brings in a new investor to cover her debts. The enigmatic buyer announces his plans to restructure SofiX and the stress takes a toll on Sofia's health. Marcello discovers Sofia has been hiding two important secrets from him.
